# Google Maps API Key for Frontend
# Get your API key from: https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 1. Go to Google Cloud Console
# 2. Create/select project
# 3. Enable "Maps JavaScript API"
# 4. Enable "Places API"
# 5. Enable "Geocoding API"
# 6. Enable billing for the project
# 7. Create API key
# 8. Set referrer restrictions to include: localhost:3000
# 9. Replace the placeholder below with your real API key

